summary.span: 提供有关 ASP.NET 身份验证失败的信息。

span.span: Provides information about ASP.NET authentication failures.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 以下列表介绍的功能为其默认情况下，asp.net 引发事件。The following list describes the features for which events are raised by default by ASP.NET. > [!NOTE] > 默认情况下 ASP.NET 配置登录审核失败条件唯一，因为记录成功的情况会严重损害系统资源。By default ASP.NET is configured to log audit failure conditions only, as logging success conditions can severely strain system resources. 你可以始终将系统配置为记录成功的情况。You can always configure the system to log the success conditions. - 窗体身份验证。Forms Authentication. 成功审核，包括进行身份验证的用户名称失败审核不包括用户名称，因为它们通常导致解密或验证失败的票证。While success audits include the user name that was authenticated; failure audits do not include the user name, since they typically result from a ticket that failed decryption or validation. 两者均包含客户端 IP 地址。Both contain the client IP address. 相关的事件审核代码是。The related event audit code is . - 成员身份。Membership. 成功和失败审核包含已尝试的用户名。Both success and failure audits contain the username that was attempted. 审核的任何一种形式将包含已尝试的密码，因为的存在风险持久保存在日志中有效的密码。Neither form of audit will contain the password that was attempted, because that would risk persisting a valid password in the log. 相关的事件审核代码是。The related event audit code is . 当引发时，默认情况下它会更新审核身份验证失败的事件引发的性能计数器。When a is raised, by default it updates the Audit Authentication Failure Events Raised performance counter. 若要查看此性能计数器在系统监视器 (PerfMon) 中**添加计数器**窗口中选择`ASP.NET`中**性能**对象下拉列表中，选择**身份验证失败的事件引发**性能计数器，然后单击**添加**按钮。To view this performance counter in System Monitor (PerfMon), in the **Add Counters** window select `ASP.NET` in the **Performance** object drop-down list, select the **Authentication Failure Events Raised** performance counter, and click the **Add** button. 有关详细信息，请参阅[ASP.NET 应用程序中使用系统监视器 (PerfMon)](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=36882&clcid=0x409) MSDN 上。For more information, see [Using the System Monitor (PerfMon) with ASP.NET Applications](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=36882&clcid=0x409) on MSDN. > [!NOTE] > 在大多数情况下你将能够实现时，使用 ASP.NET 运行状况监视类型，你将通过指定中的值来控制运行状况监视系统`healthMonitoring`配置节。In most cases you will be able to use the ASP.NET health-monitoring types as implemented, and you will control the health-monitoring system by specifying values in the `healthMonitoring` configuration section. 您还可以从要创建你自己的自定义事件和提供程序的运行状况监视类型派生。You can also derive from the health-monitoring types to create your own custom events and providers. 有关示例的派生自类，请参阅本主题中提供的示例。For an example of deriving from the class, see the example provided in this topic. ## Examples 下面的代码示例演示如何使用 类。The following code example shows how to use the class.
